Version 2.23.1
--------------

New features:

	* Cursor animation.
	* Add simple line drawing for gesture mode.

Misc improvements/fixes:

	* Move to dbus-glib.
	* Use new 'show-page' option of mouse capplet.
	* Improve secondary clicks on gnome-panel.
	
Bug fixes:

	#525032: Fix --as-needed linking.

New and updated translations:

	- [cs] Adrian Gunis
	- [de] Hendrik Brandt
	- [es] Jorge Gonzalez
	- [nn] Eskild Hustvedt
	- [sl] Matej Urbančič

